    {
      "id": "686188",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "fb_china_today",
        "uid": "8633"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t严肃的事情本来就应该是娱乐的对象<br/>\n<br/>\n这是喜剧理论里面讲的<br/>\n<br/>\n越庄严越好笑<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/id-4931__sort_key-add_time__sort-ASC\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/id-4931__sort_key-add_time__sort-ASC\">中國為什麼很少有解放軍為題材的喜劇片？</a><br/>\n<br/>\n共产党自己把现实变成喜剧, 很多中国人深受其害所以察觉不到喜剧色彩可以理解\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-09-04",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 1,
      "discussions": [
